text: Zoe Uphill (born 8 September 1982 in Canberra, Australian Capital Territory, Australia) is an Australian rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls at the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Australian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Canberra Category:1982 births Category:Australian netball players Category:Sydney Sandpipers players Category:Australian Institute of Sport netball players
